import React from 'react' const Statistics = props => { debugger const formatNumber = number => { if (isNan(number)) { return ' '} const numberArry = number.toString().split('.') numberArry[0] = numberArry[0].replace(/\B(?=(\d{3})+(?!\d))/g, ',') return numberArry.join('.') } return(
Exchange {props.data.exchange}
52 Week High {props.data.fifty_two_week_high}
Date {props.data.fifty_two_week_high_date}
52 Week Low {props.data.fifty_two_week_low}
Date {props.data.fifty_two_week_low_date}
) } export default Statistics
